The paper proposes a visual odometry method for endoscopic capsule robot operations using deep recurrent convolutional neural networks. This involves the use of computer vision and machine learning techniques, which are commonly associated with the computer science sub-categories of robotics (cs.RO), computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
